1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,285
Here are the rules you must obey when you normalize a relation.

2
00:00:04,285 --> 00:00:07,630
First, no redundancy of facts.

3
00:00:07,630 --> 00:00:11,410
Second, no cluttering of facts.

4
00:00:11,410 --> 00:00:14,580
Third, you must preserve information.

5
00:00:14,580 --> 00:00:19,210
And fourth, you must preserve functional dependencies.

